data.description: Nestled in a picturesque cul-de-sac, this exquisite residence offers a truly unique vantage point with sweeping views of the lush golf course. Step into a 2-bedroom, 2-bath upper unit featuring the elegance of vaulted ceilings in the spacious living room. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is a testament to modern design, boasting an expansive layout with gleaming laminate floors and updated cabinetry.    As you enter, you're welcomed by an abundance of natural light, courtesy of a charming sky-lit foyer. The generous balcony provides an ideal space for outdoor relaxation and al fresco dining. To complete the package, an attached garage stands ready to shelter your vehicle and offer the utmost convenience. This property promises not only a home but a lifestyle defined by tranquility and scenic beauty.
